examples.en: With 20 girls and 10 boys in the class, girls outnumber boys by 2 to 1.
No matter where you go bicycle touring, the uphills always seem to outnumber the downhills.
He was besieging an army far outnumbering his own.
Men in prison vastly outnumber women.
Owing to these causes, they soon considerably outnumber and override the trout.
